		(property "Description_1" "The Arduino UNO R4 WiFi features a 32-bit Renesas RA4M1 microcontroller (48 MHz ARM Cortex M4) and ESP32-S3-MINI-1-N8 WiFi module. The board features enhanced memory specifications with 256kB flash, 32kB SRAM, and 8kB EEPROM, while supporting both WiFi (802.11 b/g/n) and Bluetooth® 5.x connectivity at 2.4GHz. This combination of features makes it a versatile platform for wireless communication projects and IoT applications, offering significantly more processing power and connectivity options than previous UNO models."
